        <abstract> 
<p>Asks CD to have stereotype plates made of new edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> [5th English], if type still standing, though Appleton will reset type if necessary. Warns there is smaller audience in the U. S. for "good scientific books".</p>  
<p>Appleton would also like plates made of new book [<hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>] when possible.</p> 
        </abstract>
